children.name: Cookbook Loaded
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "Loading cookbooks" 
| parse "cookbooks [*]" as cookbooks
| parse regex  field=cookbooks "(?<cookbook>[^, \]]+)" multi 
| count_distinct(cookbook) by _sourceHost

children.name: Exceptions by Host
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=chef* Exception*
| parse regex "host=(?<src_host>[^&]+)&ip_address=(?<src_ip>[^&]+)&"  
| parse "Full list: *" as exceptions | urldecode(exceptions) as exceptions

children.name: Handler-Based Chef Run Report
children.description: This dashboard requires data by SumoLogic chef Handler

panels.name: Top 10 Most Updated Resources
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "completed successfully" !"Logfile created"
| parse "updated_resources=*" as resources 
| concat(resources," ") as resources
| parse  regex field=resources "(?<resource>\S+)\s"  multi  nodrop 
| count as Count by resource  | top 10 resource by Count

panels.name: Run Duration Distribution Overtime
panels.queryString:
$$Chef  "chef*-Client" "elapsed_time"
| parse "chef*-Client *:" as msg
| if (msg matches "*completed successfully*", "success", "failed") as status 
| parse "elapsed_time=*&" as runtime 
| 5 as bucket_size
| long(runtime/bucket_size) as range | format("%d-%d",long(range*bucket_size), long((range+1)*bucket_size)) as bucket
| count as Runs by bucket, status,range
| sort by range | fields -range
| transpose row bucket column status 
| sort by bucket

panels.name: Updated Resources Overtime
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "completed successfully" 
| parse "updated_resources=*" as resources 
| concat(resources,":") as resources
| parse  regex field=resources "(?<resource>\S+)\s"  multi
| timeslice 1h  
| count by _timeslice, resource
| transpose row _timeslice column resource

panels.name: Failed Runs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "chef*-Client" "did not complete" 
| parse regex "host=(?<src_host>[^&]+)&ip_address=(?<src_ip>[^&]+)&" 
| parse "end_time=*&" as end_time 
| count by src_host, src_ip, end_time,_messagetime,_raw
| sort by -_messagetime |  fields - _raw, _messagetime, _count  |  "chef*-Client did not complete" as message

panels.name: Average Runtime by Host
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "completed successfully" 
| parse regex "host=(?<src_host>[^&]+)&ip_address=(?<src_ip>[^&]+)&"  
| parse "elapsed_time=*&" as runtime 
| avg(runtime) by src_host

panels.name: Run Status Overtime
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  
| parse "chef*-Client *:" as msg
| if (msg matches "*completed successfully*", "success", "failed") as status 
| timeslice 1h 
| count by status,_timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column status

panels.name: Average RunTime by Host (Seconds)
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef* "chef* Run complete"
| parse "in * seconds" as runtime  
| avg(runtime) as AvgRunTime by _sourceHost
| sort by AvgRunTime

panels.name: Host Count by Error or Fatal Message
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef* ("error" or "fatal") !"WARN:"
| parse "] *" as message 
| count_distinct (_sourceHost) as Hosts by message  | order by Hosts

panels.name: Host Count by Cookbook
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "Loading cookbooks" 
| parse "cookbooks [*]" as cookbooks
| parse regex  field=cookbooks "(?<cookbook>[^, \]]+)" multi 
| count by _sourceHost,cookbook
| count(_sourceHost) as hosts by cookbook 
| sort hosts

panels.name: Run Duration Distribution
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef* "chef* Run complete"
| parse "in * seconds" as runtime
| 5 as bucket_size
| long(runtime/bucket_size) as range | format("%d-%d",long(range*bucket_size), long((range+1)*bucket_size)) as bucket
| count as Runs by bucket,range
| sort by range | fields -range
| sort by +bucket

panels.name: Hosts with Potential Failed Runs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=chef* ("Starting chef* Run for"  or "chef* Run complete") 
| if (_raw matches "*Starting chef* Run*", "Started", "Completed") as status
| count by status,_sourceHost 
| sort by _sourceHost, status
| diff _count by _sourceHost 
| where _diff>0 
| (_diff+_count) as  Started 
| _count as Completed | fields -status,_count, _diff

panels.name: Error or Fatal Count by Host

children.name: Resource Extraction
children.searchQuery:
_sourceCategory=chef*  "completed successfully" 
| parse "updated_resources=*" as resources 
| concat(resources,":") as resources
| parse  regex field=resources "(?<resource>\S+)\s"  multi
